{"tid":569680,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"雞，真係家禽之霸","createTime":"2018-02-23T02:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T08:10:50.000Z","uid":82002,"like":1326,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"529585402f65c7e4a020fb77db408b327bb5423a","tid":569680,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:23:00.000Z","msg":"有無人鍾意食雞去到一個返唔到轉頭既地步？<br />\n鍾意食既人自然會明，<br />\n一隻雞落係十個唔同廚師既手中，<br />\n就會衍生出十種唔同既做法。<br />\n雞，唔似得豬，牛，羊，<br />\n佢地多數既做法都係獨孤一味，<br />\n而且各自有唔同既缺點。<br />\n就同揀女一樣。<br />\n牛，多數都係煎牛排，燒牛肉，熱氣而性毒。<br />\n如一個偽ABC，雖然貴氣，但難以時常食用。<br />\n豬，雖然較為多元化，但都難登大雅之堂。<br />\n好似大陸妹，雖然身材正又肯玩，但始終有文化之別。<br />\n羊，可供選擇少，而且好多人接受唔到佢既騷味。<br />\n如同一個性格公主既港女，唔係人人伺候得起。<br />\n<br />\n反觀雞就可以將以上全部秒殺，<br />\n雞唔單止多元化，蒸，煮，炒，焗，燉，炸，煎，釀，<br />\n無論南北菜系，中西餐廳，<br />\n雞往往都係主菜入面最閃亮的星。<br />\n猶如一個任勞任怨，千變萬化，<br />\n入得廚房，出得天堂既賢良老婆。<br />\n蒸白切雞滑，煎雞腿肉香，煮雞煲刺激，<br />\n炸雞脆，焗雞嫩而多汁，燉雞湯滋補。<br />\n<br />\n雞，無愧係家禽之霸。<br />\n<br />\n（各位巴絲，其實我都係想乞下，有無好食既雞推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）你比個地方，我去食再出專業雞評！"},{"pid":"f4b4e92a1013b5a26ddbc9b9b4e2f7e6be2c35cc","tid":569680,"uid":61300,"like":347,"dislike":8,"score":339,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:24:21.000Z","msg":"KFC"},{"pid":"6dc3261ce8af7abe1173ed95ef0116ae6aa4a1cf","tid":569680,"uid":56240,"like":7,"dislike":50,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"港女係羊？<br />\n都是雞！"},{"pid":"06956c4a5b9b8f8158e272f8bc1af42a0938036f","tid":569680,"uid":82002,"like":209,"dislike":4,"score":205,"quote":{"pid":"6dc3261ce8af7abe1173ed95ef0116ae6aa4a1cf","tid":569680,"uid":56240,"like":7,"dislike":50,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"港女係羊？<br />\n都是雞！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"唔好咁樣話啲雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b73ea88ea68988d4e82f9f326dae63019d0ea90","tid":569680,"uid":82002,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"f4b4e92a1013b5a26ddbc9b9b4e2f7e6be2c35cc","tid":569680,"uid":61300,"like":347,"dislike":8,"score":339,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:24:21.000Z","msg":"KFC"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"無乜誠意啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d164d5bb7ae84ecb47e90465e3f840a54aafcbb","tid":569680,"uid":65686,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"港女，真係家禽之霸"},{"pid":"fbe4c47f10f3accbad42274af87de4bce3f470f5","tid":569680,"uid":105907,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"大陸走地雞 真心正"},{"pid":"13c92a65ceab207bd8a2c88a1941d529d5141355","tid":569680,"uid":82002,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbe4c47f10f3accbad42274af87de4bce3f470f5","tid":569680,"uid":105907,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"大陸走地雞 真心正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"香港邊度有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b4111cea8eead4a697a7d70ec44085d68fa18f","tid":569680,"uid":8727,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"好雞真係要返大陸先食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ba81f5f5af45a2ed57621d7081aa5fe5f65974","tid":569680,"uid":74293,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"觀塘開左檔叫清遠雞<br />\n係堅走地雞 <br />\n皮爽肉滑<br />\n好食"},{"pid":"ec0226b630b13b8e15ff89e550e5c72cd83afec3","tid":569680,"uid":105907,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大陸走地雞 真心正</blockquote>香港邊度有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無 要返深圳買"},{"pid":"2e1c5d245642d59446590449470e440b220f37a5","tid":569680,"uid":66099,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"生叮雞<img src=\"/